flowchart TD

    %% Login process
    A[Start: Open StegCrypt] --> B{Fingerprint Login Successful?}
    B -- Yes --> C[Access Granted → Show GUI]
    B -- No --> D{Username & Password Correct?}
    D -- Yes --> C
    D -- No --> E[Access Denied → Retry Login]

    %% Encryption process
    C --> F[User selects Encryption Tool]
    F --> G[Select file to encrypt]
    G --> H{File size between 50MB and 100MB?}
    H -- No --> I[Error: File must be 50–100MB] --> C
    H -- Yes --> J[Encrypt File]
    J --> K[Encryption Complete] --> C

    %% Decryption process (system check only)
    C --> L[User selects Decryption Tool]
    L --> M[Select file]
    M --> N{System detects: File is encrypted?}
    N -- No --> O[Error: Not an encrypted file] --> C
    N -- Yes --> P[Decrypt File]
    P --> Q[Decryption Complete] --> C

    %% Steganography process - Hide
    C --> R[User selects Steganography Tool → Hide]
    R --> S[Select cover image]
    S --> T[Select file to hide]
    T --> U[Hide File in Image]
    U --> V[Steganography Complete] --> C

    %% Steganography process - Reveal (system check only)
    C --> W[User selects Steganography Tool → Reveal]
    W --> X[Select image file]
    X --> Y{System detects: Hidden data found?}
    Y -- No --> Z[Error: No hidden data in image] --> C
    Y -- Yes --> AA[Reveal Hidden File]
    AA --> AB[Reveal Complete] --> C





